{"tid":1936771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印度人飲牛尿，食牛屎來預防武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-21T12:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T14:06:01.000Z","uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"267925ba4e005ee98d0daf56d91844f5978a33e7","tid":1936771,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ArQ1CrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArQ1CrR.png&h=dcdc427a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有印度教信徒認為喝牛尿可以對抗新冠病毒，同時淨化身心靈。他們堅信牛尿能消滅細菌，一直以來都有用牛尿作為家中的消毒劑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/news/amp/world-asia-india-51910099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fworld-asia-india-51910099&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=7e827a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/news/amp/world-asia-india-51910099</a><br />\n<br />\n平時屎尿都敢擺入口，病毒算得啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e984faf1aa351755e8c7c9ac638696b33deb99","tid":1936771,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱食完飯見到個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217522fcf3f6bb232105534204c42917885c611e","tid":1936771,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e984faf1aa351755e8c7c9ac638696b33deb99","tid":1936771,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱食完飯見到個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係食飯前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c44c3b5b68990c37927b7b0c30c88ef7a7cda0","tid":1936771,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"如果堅有效，你估你唔去飲咩<img sr